Renae Jacobs https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renae_Jacobs 0 Renae Jacobs (born February 1, 1957) is an American voice actress who is perhaps best known for voicing journalist and reporter April O'Neil in the original Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles animated series.
